{"type":"session_message","session_id":"ses_28c6e0507ffeaXxTAMFtC4gCYu","role":"assistant","message_id":"msg_d7397072c001K9Q8i0fsNIR85F","parts":[{"id":"prt_d73970edc001DkmJpK2N2BfL6a","messageID":"msg_d7397072c001K9Q8i0fsNIR85F","sessionID":"ses_28c6e0507ffeaXxTAMFtC4gCYu","type":"text","text":"## 仓库配置任务完成报告\n\n### 仓库信息\n- **仓库**: poetry (python-poetry/poetry)\n- **版本**: 2.4.0.dev0\n- **Python 版本**: 3.11.2\n\n### 已执行的关键步骤\n\n#### 1. 环境准备\n- 安装 `python3-pip`, `python3-venv`\n- 安装 `pipx` 用于管理 Poetry\n- 使用 pipx 安装 Poetry 2.3.3\n\n#### 2. Poetry 配置\n```bash\npoetry config virtualenvs.use-poetry-python false\npoetry config virtualenvs.in-project true\n```\n\n#### 3. 依赖安装\n```bash\npoetry install --with test,typing\n```\n- 安装 71 个依赖包\n- 创建虚拟环境于 `/workspace/.venv`\n\n#### 4. 验证命令及结果\n\n| 验证命令 | 结果 |\n|---------|------|\n| `poetry check --lock` | ✅ All set! |\n| `poetry run mypy src/poetry` | ✅ 无错误 |\n| `pytest tests/json/test_schema.py` | ✅ 7 passed |\n| `pytest tests/puzzle/test_transaction.py` | ✅ 89 passed |\n| `pytest tests/console/commands/test_version.py` | ✅ 36 passed |\n| `pytest tests/puzzle/` | ✅ 349 passed |\n| `pytest tests/installation/` | ✅ 610 passed, 1 skipped |\n| `pytest tests/repositories/` | ✅ 285 passed |\n| `pytest tests/console/` | ✅ 928 passed, 6 skipped |\n| `pytest tests/mixology/` | ✅ 46 passed |\n| `pytest tests/plugins/ tests/publishing/ tests/config/` | ✅ 172 passed |\n\n#### 5. 已知问题\n运行全量测试时发现 1 个失败：\n- `tests/utils/test_threading.py::test_threading_atomic_cached_property_different_instances[value_functools_cache-392]`\n- **原因**: 这是一个与 xdist 并行测试执行相关的竞争条件问题，测试期望 `functools.cache` 在 192 个工作进程下被调用 392 次，但实际调用次数因线程调度而异。这是测试本身的稳定性问题，不是环境配置问题。\n\n### 最终状态\n✅ **环境配置成功**\n\n- Poetry 2.3.3 已安装并可正常运行\n- 虚拟环境已创建并激活\n- 所有开发和测试依赖已安装\n- 核心测试套件验证通过（超过 2500 个测试通过）\n- Mypy 类型检查通过","time":{"start":1775760783922,"end":1775760783922}}]}
